{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":827,"text":"I've always written primarily about architecture,"},{"time":2858,"text":"about buildings, and writing about architecture"},{"time":5383,"text":"is based on certain assumptions."},{"time":8124,"text":"An architect designs a building, and it becomes a place,"},{"time":10582,"text":"or many architects design many buildings, and it becomes"},{"time":13062,"text":"a city, and regardless of this complicated mix of forces"},{"time":16336,"text":"of politics and culture and economics that shapes"},{"time":18733,"text":"these places, at the end of the day, you can go"},{"time":21736,"text":"and you can visit them. You can walk around them."},{"time":24392,"text":"You can smell them. You can get a feel for them."},{"time":26065,"text":"You can experience their sense of place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29558,"text":"But what was striking to me over the last several years"},{"time":31907,"text":"was that less and less was I going out into the world,"},{"time":35282,"text":"and more and more, I was sitting in front of my computer screen."},{"time":38511,"text":"And especially since about 2007, when I got an iPhone,"},{"time":42831,"text":"I was not only sitting in front of my screen all day,"},{"time":44707,"text":"but I was also getting up at the end of the day"},{"time":46804,"text":"and looking at this little screen that I carried in my pocket."},{"time":50104,"text":"And what was surprising to me was how quickly"},{"time":52963,"text":"my relationship to the physical world had changed."},{"time":55900,"text":"In this very short period of time, you know, whether you"},{"time":57675,"text":"call it the last 15 years or so of being online, or the last,"},{"time":61131,"text":"you know, four or five years of being online all the time,"},{"time":64090,"text":"our relationship to our surroundings had changed in that"},{"time":67264,"text":"our attention is constantly divided. You know,"},{"time":69063,"text":"we're both looking inside the screens and we're looking"},{"time":71627,"text":"out in the world around us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73459,"text":"And what was even more striking to me, and what I really"},{"time":75986,"text":"got hung up on, was that the world inside the screen"},{"time":78988,"text":"seemed to have no physical reality of its own."},{"time":82777,"text":"If you went and looked for images of the Internet,"},{"time":85545,"text":"this was all that you found, this famous image by Opte"},{"time":88663,"text":"of the Internet as the kind of Milky Way, this infinite expanse"},{"time":91793,"text":"where we don't seem to be anywhere on it."},{"time":93889,"text":"We can never seem to grasp it in its totality."},{"time":96313,"text":"It's always reminded me of the Apollo image of the Earth,"},{"time":99930,"text":"the blue marble picture, and it's similarly meant to suggest,"},{"time":102660,"text":"I think, that we can't really understand it as a whole."},{"time":105357,"text":"We're always sort of small in the face of its expanse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109042,"text":"So if there was this world and this screen, and if there was"},{"time":112407,"text":"the physical world around me, I couldn't ever get them"},{"time":115264,"text":"together in the same place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118245,"text":"And then this happened."},{"time":121452,"text":"My Internet broke one day, as it occasionally does,"},{"time":124050,"text":"and the cable guy came to fix it, and he started with"},{"time":126784,"text":"the dusty clump of cables behind the couch,"},{"time":128911,"text":"and he followed it to the front of my building and into the basement and out to the back yard,"},{"time":132121,"text":"and there was this big jumble of cables against the wall."},{"time":134997,"text":"And then he saw a squirrel running along the wire,"},{"time":137551,"text":"and he said, \"There's your problem."},{"time":140342,"text":"A squirrel is chewing on your Internet.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":144763,"text":"And this seemed astounding. The Internet is"},{"time":147890,"text":"a transcendent idea. It's a set of protocols that has changed"},{"time":151264,"text":"everything from shopping to dating to revolutions."},{"time":154719,"text":"It was unequivocally not something"},{"time":157348,"text":"a squirrel could chew on. (Laughter)"},{"time":160659,"text":"But that in fact seemed to be the case."},{"time":162537,"text":"A squirrel had in fact chewed on my Internet. (Laughter)"},{"time":165739,"text":"And then I got this image in my head of what would happen"},{"time":167926,"text":"if you yanked the wire from the wall and if you started"},{"time":170106,"text":"to follow it. Where would it go?"},{"time":171710,"text":"Was the Internet actually a place that you could visit?"},{"time":175218,"text":"Could I go there? Who would I meet?"},{"time":176567,"text":"You know, was there something actually out there?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":179943,"text":"And the answer, by all accounts, was no."},{"time":182980,"text":"This was the Internet, this black box with a red light on it,"},{"time":185760,"text":"as represented in the sitcom \"The IT Crowd.\""},{"time":189190,"text":"Normally it lives on the top of Big Ben,"},{"time":192749,"text":"because that's where you get the best reception,"},{"time":195831,"text":"but they had negotiated that their colleague could borrow it"},{"time":199136,"text":"for the afternoon to use in an office presentation."},{"time":202308,"text":"The elders of the Internet were willing to part with it"},{"time":204682,"text":"for a short while, and she looks at it and she says,"},{"time":207548,"text":"\"This is the Internet? The whole Internet? Is it heavy?\""},{"time":210938,"text":"They say, \"Of course not, the Internet doesn't weigh anything.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":214898,"text":"And I was embarrassed. I was looking for this thing"},{"time":217215,"text":"that only fools seem to look for."},{"time":219511,"text":"The Internet was that amorphous blob, or it was a silly"},{"time":222346,"text":"black box with a blinking red light on it."},{"time":224592,"text":"It wasn't a real world out there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226920,"text":"But, in fact, it is. There is a real world of the Internet out there,"},{"time":230232,"text":"and that's what I spent about two years visiting,"},{"time":231998,"text":"these places of the Internet. I was in large data centers"},{"time":235543,"text":"that use as much power as the cities in which they sit,"},{"time":238188,"text":"and I visited places like this, 60 Hudson Street in New York,"},{"time":241377,"text":"which is one of the buildings in the world,"},{"time":243085,"text":"one of a very short list of buildings, about a dozen buildings,"},{"time":245983,"text":"where more networks of the Internet connect to each other"},{"time":248627,"text":"than anywhere else."},{"time":249985,"text":"And that connection is an unequivocally physical process."},{"time":252602,"text":"It's about the router of one network, a Facebook or"},{"time":255087,"text":"a Google or a B.T. or a Comcast or a Time Warner, whatever it is,"},{"time":258029,"text":"connecting with usually a yellow fiber optic cable up into"},{"time":260460,"text":"the ceiling and down into the router of another network,"},{"time":263154,"text":"and that's unequivocally physical, and it's surprisingly intimate."},{"time":267531,"text":"A building like 60 Hudson, and a dozen or so others,"},{"time":270824,"text":"has 10 times more networks connecting within it"},{"time":273150,"text":"than the next tier of buildings."},{"time":274998,"text":"There's a very short list of these places."},{"time":277066,"text":"And 60 Hudson in particular is interesting because it's home"},{"time":279974,"text":"to about a half a dozen very important networks,"},{"time":282563,"text":"which are the networks which serve the undersea cables"},{"time":284861,"text":"that travel underneath the ocean"},{"time":287209,"text":"that connect Europe and America and connect all of us."},{"time":289462,"text":"And it's those cables in particular that I want to focus on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293049,"text":"If the Internet is a global phenomenon, if we live"},{"time":296925,"text":"in a global village, it's because there are cables underneath"},{"time":299365,"text":"the ocean, cables like this."},{"time":301470,"text":"And in this dimension, they are incredibly small."},{"time":304356,"text":"You can you hold them in your hand. They're like a garden hose."},{"time":307298,"text":"But in the other dimension they are incredibly expansive,"},{"time":311361,"text":"as expansive as you can imagine."},{"time":313001,"text":"They stretch across the ocean. They're three or five"},{"time":315556,"text":"or eight thousand miles in length, and"},{"time":318167,"text":"if the material science and the computational technology"},{"time":320776,"text":"is incredibly complicated, the basic physical process"},{"time":324309,"text":"is shockingly simple. Light goes in on one end of the ocean"},{"time":328089,"text":"and comes out on the other, and it usually comes"},{"time":331374,"text":"from a building called a landing station that's often"},{"time":334007,"text":"tucked away inconspicuously in a little seaside neighborhood,"},{"time":336954,"text":"and there are amplifiers that sit on the ocean floor"},{"time":339688,"text":"that look kind of like bluefin tuna, and every 50 miles"},{"time":342208,"text":"they amplify the signal, and since the rate of transmission"},{"time":345865,"text":"is incredibly fast, the basic unit is a 10-gigabit-per-second"},{"time":349071,"text":"wavelength of light, maybe a thousand times your own"},{"time":351569,"text":"connection, or capable of carrying 10,000 video streams,"},{"time":354753,"text":"but not only that, but you'll put not just one wavelength of light"},{"time":358031,"text":"through one of the fibers, but you'll put maybe"},{"time":360988,"text":"50 or 60 or 70 different wavelengths or colors of light"},{"time":364007,"text":"through a single fiber, and then you'll have maybe"},{"time":366875,"text":"eight fibers in a cable, four going in each direction."},{"time":369477,"text":"And they're tiny. They're the thickness of a hair."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372967,"text":"And then they connect to the continent somewhere."},{"time":374796,"text":"They connect in a manhole like this. Literally,"},{"time":377134,"text":"this is where the 5,000-mile cable plugs in."},{"time":380223,"text":"This is in Halifax, a cable that stretches from Halifax to Ireland."},{"time":384713,"text":"And the landscape is changing. Three years ago,"},{"time":387694,"text":"when I started thinking about this, there was one cable"},{"time":389590,"text":"down the Western coast of Africa, represented"},{"time":392757,"text":"in this map by Steve Song as that thin black line."},{"time":395631,"text":"Now there are six cables and more coming, three down each coast."},{"time":400476,"text":"Because once a country gets plugged in by one cable,"},{"time":403107,"text":"they realize that it's not enough. If they're going to build"},{"time":404907,"text":"an industry around it, they need to know that their connection"},{"time":407723,"text":"isn't tenuous but permanent, because if a cable breaks,"},{"time":410433,"text":"you have to send a ship out into the water, throw"},{"time":412500,"text":"a grappling hook over the side, pick it up, find the other end,"},{"time":415415,"text":"and then fuse the two ends back together and then dump it over."},{"time":418458,"text":"It's an intensely, intensely physical process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":422998,"text":"So this is my friend Simon Cooper, who until very recently"},{"time":427296,"text":"worked for Tata Communications, the communications wing"},{"time":429968,"text":"of Tata, the big Indian industrial conglomerate."},{"time":432966,"text":"And I've never met him. We've only communicated"},{"time":435948,"text":"via this telepresence system, which always makes me"},{"time":439405,"text":"think of him as the man inside the Internet. (Laughter)"},{"time":443301,"text":"And he is English. The undersea cable industry"},{"time":446498,"text":"is dominated by Englishmen, and they all seem to be 42."},{"time":450143,"text":"(Laughter) Because they all started at the same time"},{"time":453318,"text":"with the boom about 20 years ago."},{"time":455818,"text":"And Tata had gotten its start as a communications business"},{"time":459078,"text":"when they bought two cables, one across the Atlantic"},{"time":461543,"text":"and one across the Pacific, and proceeded to add pieces"},{"time":464703,"text":"onto them, until they had built a belt around the world,"},{"time":468247,"text":"which means they will send your bits to the East or the West."},{"time":470344,"text":"They have -- this is literally a beam of light around the world,"},{"time":472567,"text":"and if a cable breaks in the Pacific, it'll send it around"},{"time":474778,"text":"the other direction. And then having done that,"},{"time":477963,"text":"they started to look for places to wire next."},{"time":481907,"text":"They looked for the unwired places, and that's meant"},{"time":484397,"text":"North and South, primarily these cables to Africa."},{"time":487191,"text":"But what amazes me is Simon's incredible geographic imagination."},{"time":490962,"text":"He thinks about the world with this incredible expansiveness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493921,"text":"And I was particularly interested because I wanted to see"},{"time":497234,"text":"one of these cables being built. See, you know, all the time"},{"time":500086,"text":"online we experience these fleeting moments of connection,"},{"time":502406,"text":"these sort of brief adjacencies, a tweet or a Facebook post"},{"time":505700,"text":"or an email, and it seemed like there was a physical corollary to that."},{"time":509540,"text":"It seemed like there was a moment when the continent"},{"time":511616,"text":"was being plugged in, and I wanted to see that."},{"time":513963,"text":"And Simon was working on a new cable,"},{"time":516248,"text":"WACS, the West Africa Cable System, that stretched"},{"time":518759,"text":"from Lisbon down the west coast of Africa,"},{"time":520880,"text":"to Cote d'Ivoire, to Ghana, to Nigeria, to Cameroon."},{"time":523749,"text":"And he said there was coming soon, depending"},{"time":526082,"text":"on the weather, but he'd let me know when,"},{"time":528276,"text":"and so with about four days notice, he said to go"},{"time":531477,"text":"to this beach south of Lisbon, and a little after 9,"},{"time":534308,"text":"this guy will walk out of the water. (Laughter)"},{"time":538004,"text":"And he'll be carrying a green nylon line, a lightweight line,"},{"time":542324,"text":"called a messenger line, and that was the first link"},{"time":545037,"text":"between sea and land, this link that would then be"},{"time":547590,"text":"leveraged into this 9,000-mile path of light."},{"time":551453,"text":"Then a bulldozer began to pull the cable in from this"},{"time":554043,"text":"specialized cable landing ship, and it was floated"},{"time":557400,"text":"on these buoys until it was in the right place."},{"time":560148,"text":"Then you can see the English engineers looking on."},{"time":562890,"text":"And then, once it was in the right place, he got back"},{"time":565703,"text":"in the water holding a big knife, and he cut each buoy off,"},{"time":569062,"text":"and the buoy popped up into the air, and the cable"},{"time":571361,"text":"dropped to the sea floor, and he did that all the way out"},{"time":573266,"text":"to the ship, and when he got there,"},{"time":575139,"text":"they gave him a glass of juice and a cookie,"},{"time":577552,"text":"and then he jumped back in, and he swam back to shore,"},{"time":579971,"text":"and then he lit a cigarette. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":587131,"text":"And then once that cable was on shore,"},{"time":589843,"text":"they began to prepare to connect it to the other side,"},{"time":593347,"text":"for the cable that had been brought down from the landing station."},{"time":596304,"text":"And first they got it with a hacksaw, and then they start"},{"time":599162,"text":"sort of shaving away at this plastic interior with a --"},{"time":602098,"text":"sort of working like chefs, and then finally they're working"},{"time":604160,"text":"like jewelers to get these hair-thin fibers to line up"},{"time":606868,"text":"with the cable that had come down,"},{"time":608545,"text":"and with this hole-punch machine they fuse it together."},{"time":611536,"text":"And when you see these guys going at this cable with a hacksaw,"},{"time":614867,"text":"you stop thinking about the Internet as a cloud."},{"time":617510,"text":"It starts to seem like an incredibly physical thing."},{"time":621447,"text":"And what surprised me as well was that as much as this"},{"time":623955,"text":"is based on the most sophisticated technology, as much"},{"time":626802,"text":"as this is an incredibly new thing, the physical process"},{"time":629707,"text":"itself has been around for a long time, and the culture is the same."},{"time":633474,"text":"You see the local laborers. You see the English engineer"},{"time":635463,"text":"giving directions in the background. And more importantly,"},{"time":638638,"text":"the places are the same. These cables still connect"},{"time":641281,"text":"these classic port cities, places like Lisbon, Mombasa,"},{"time":644331,"text":"Mumbai, Singapore, New York."}]},{"cues":[{"time":647490,"text":"And then the process on shore takes around three or four days,"},{"time":651576,"text":"and then, when it's done, they put the manhole cover"},{"time":655767,"text":"back on top, and they push the sand over that,"},{"time":658738,"text":"and we all forget about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":661820,"text":"And it seems to me that we talk a lot about the cloud,"},{"time":664071,"text":"but every time we put something on the cloud,"},{"time":665981,"text":"we give up some responsibility for it."},{"time":668183,"text":"We are less connected to it. We let other people worry about it."},{"time":672047,"text":"And that doesn't seem right."},{"time":673330,"text":"There's a great Neal Stephenson line where he says"},{"time":675672,"text":"that wired people should know something about wires."},{"time":680069,"text":"And we should know, I think, we should know"},{"time":682339,"text":"where our Internet comes from, and we should know"},{"time":685092,"text":"what it is that physically, physically connects us all."},{"time":689914,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":692253,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":694650,"text":"Thanks. (Applause)"}]}]}